name: final-project-s23-cd-users-baddies
description: BizReach is an online platform used to connect nearby mobile businesses to customers in need of their services. It allows users to browse a variety of different services and businesses to view local customers in need of their services. Payments can be made directly on BizReach, which offers a simple and secure transaction.

scripts.start: concurrently "cd backend && npm run dev" "cd frontend && npm start"
